# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Secrets — NEVER COMMIT
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# The Ed25519 STH signing key is the single most sensitive secret in a
# deployment — never let it near version control.
*.p12
*.p8
*.cer
*.pem
*.key
*.pub
*.jks
*.keystore
ed25519*
sth-signing*
log-private*
service-account*.json
authkey*.json
credentials.*
secrets/
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

